About
MrClicky Ver 1.a
A simple program allowing rapid fire from most keys or mouse buttons, good when coupled with Gnome Sequencer in WOW but can be used with any game as it simulates keypresses or mouse button clicks. I also added a feature to fire your combo points by reading when the fith one is filled. Pick the key you want it to trigger then add a macro to your bar in game and bind that key to it for the spell to fire. Add some checking like [combat][@tar [rest of string was truncated]";.
